Description: The President's Information Technology Advisory Committee (PITAC) was authorized by Congress
Headquarters Regions: Washington DC Metro Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: The President's Information Technology Advisory Committee (PITAC) was authorized by Congress under the High-Performance Computing Act of 1991 (P. L. 102-194) and the Next Generation Internet Act of 1998 (P. L. 105-305) as a Federal Advisory Committee. The Committee provides the President, Congress, and the Federal agencies involved in networking and information technology research and development with expert, independent advice on maintaining America's preeminence in advanced information technologies, including such critical elements of the national information technology infrastructure as high performance computing, large-scale networking, cyber security, and high assurance software and systems design. As part of this assessment, the PITAC reviews the Federal Networking and Information Technology Research and Development (NITRD) Program. Comprising leading IT experts from industry and academia, the Committee helps guide the Administration's efforts to accelerate the development and adoption of information technologies vital for American prosperity in the 21st century. Executive Order 13385 assigned the role and responsibilities of PITAC to the President's Council of Advisors on Science and Technology (PCAST).

Recognizing the evolving needs of its clients, SFK Inc. underwent a transformative evolution in 2010, becoming a parent company that expanded its service offerings to meet the demands of a growing clientele. In 2015, the company further solidified its position in the market by establishing SFK Security Consultants (SFK SecCon), a specialist division offering security, operations, and strategic consulting services. SFK Inc. stands out in the industry due to its tailored approach and exceptional customer service. The company's management team and board members are actively involved in multiple projects, ensuring personalized attention and real-time awareness of each operation's progress. With a focus on client satisfaction, SFK Inc. consistently exceeds expectations, providing cutting-edge solutions to address complex challenges. The team at SFK Inc. comprises a diverse group of highly skilled professionals, including process, chemical, and marine engineers, management consultants, master mariners, inspectors, data scientists, and investigators. This collective expertise positions SFK Inc. at the forefront of the industry, equipped to deliver innovative solutions that meet and surpass client expectations. With over four decades of combined experience in their sectors, SFK Inc. goes above and beyond to provide exceptional services. Leveraging a vast global network and strategic partnerships, the company is well-equipped to serve clients across diverse industries and locations worldwide. SFK Inc. leverages advanced technologies such as AI and ML to enhance antiquated industries, giving their services and clients a competitive edge. As a trusted partner in navigating the complex business landscape, SFK Inc. remains dedicated to delivering industry expertise, comprehensive solutions, and an unwavering commitment to excellence.

If you are looking to schedule your surgery, we invite you to contact us by calling one of our skilled administrators will be happy to assist you. POMPANO BEACH SURGICAL CENTER A significant advantage of opting for a surgery center is the absence of an overnight hospital stay.
